title: Pics: We're just a little bit in lurve with Michelle Keegan's new Lipsy Collection
text:
Michelle Keegan has collaboration with the Queens of festive glitz - that being Lipsy - with a brand new collection just in time for the Christmas party season - HOLLAH!
Speaking of their perfect union, the Lipsy Website says "Thereâ€™s a beautiful dress for every occasion in this glamorous range, and our sophisticated separates will see you through the next season in style. Bring the wow factor to an evening event in a jaw-dropping maxi number or achieve minimalist chic in a figure-hugging crop top and skirt co-ord."
While you can view the full collection in all its loveliness here via Lipsy.co.uk , below we've trawled through the countless looks to bring you our five favourite outfits.
OK, it's impossible to stick to just five - check out this coat for flip's sake, and that's just one of many coats on offer.
